Napoli beat Cagliari 3-0 in Serie A on Sunday afternoon . 
  Jose Callejon opened the scoring for Rafa Benitez side . 
  Antonio Balzano scored an own goal for the away side . 
  Manolo Gabbiadini added a third for the Partenopei . 
  Napoli are fourth in the Serie A table and are in the hunt for Champions League qualification . 
 